<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="comment-n">comment <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒment/    美 /'kɑːment/  </p>
<p>(remark)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 评论：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>no comment</strong>
无可奉告</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is impolite to <strong>make</strong> unfavourable <strong>comments on</strong> a person’s appearance. 
对他人的外貌作负面评价是不礼貌的。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 2</footer></div></div>